data.description: Beautiful 4 bedrm 2.5 bath home! The floorplan is open and flowing, the lot is one of the best in the neighborhood. Efficient home, gas for heat, hot water and the fireplace, all lighting is LED, energy and utility costs are below average. The fully fenced back yard is very functional and a beautiful place to escape the day under the patio or around the firepit! The yard is beautifully landscaped and features a variety of mature evergreen trees for privacy, ornamental bananas, Japanese red maple and many varieties of wildflowers. The inside is filled with natural light throughout the day. The 9-foot ceilings and new continuous floors make the main level feel very inviting. The garage has great lighting, extra storage shelving, workbench and an epoxy floor. Property has been transformed w/ many updates and upgrades, New roof 2022, New Trane high efficiency HVAC 2022, new toilets, main lvl new paint top to bottom, most of the upper lvl  freshly painted, LVP flooring main lvl 2023.
